es.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Jul 2022) 0aDiplomatszUnited StatesvBiographyvSources. 7aHISTORY / World.2bisacsh  aBiography, Diplomatic history, Europe, Foreign relations, Hungary, United States, World War II.1 aFrank, Tibor, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFrank, Tibor, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertCentral European University Press eBook-Package 2013-1998z978311078055040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978615521106540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9786155211065423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9786155211065/original  a978-3-11-078055-0  Central European University Press eBook-Package 2013-1998c1998d2013  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_HICS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK